			<change xml:lang="EN">
				<p sameAs="title">Note from Miranda to Félix João Freire Corte-Real, a major.</p>
				<p sameAs="summary">The author tells the addressee that he will proceed as previously arranged between the two of them.</p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc"> Several military men were imprisoned in Lisbon's military jail accused of political crimes, especially because of their association with the major Félix João Freire Corte-Real, described as a dangerous and revolutionary individual. Two pieces of writing (a letter and a note) between them were apprehended  inside the jail.</p>
				<p sameAs="text"></p></change>
